
Overview of noun turntable

The noun turntable has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                      
1. (1) turntable -- (a circular horizontal platform that rotates a phonograph record while it is being played)
2. turntable, lazy Susan -- (a revolving tray placed on a dining table)
3. turntable -- (a rotatable platform with a track; used to turn locomotives and cars)
